title: Did the Trump Administration Try to Deport U.S. Reps. Omar and AOC?
subtitle: A frequent producer of inflammatory misinformation published yet more junk news in July 2019.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: In July 2019, the administration of U.S. President Donald Trump initiated deportation proceedings against U.S. Reps. Ilhan Omar (D-Minn.) and Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez (D-NY).
